house job after an admittedly rocky start but now even his critics 
have had to admit he appears to be effective and may wield more 
power than any other recent chief of staff 
most republican politicians believe it is to new hampshires 
advantage to have sununu in the white house 
we may not get everything from the white house but people at 
the white house have the ear of new hampshire said bill zeliff 
a sununu ally who is seeking the gop nomination for smiths 
congressional seat 
