possibility of such a solution 
while no agreement had been reached within the 16party 
democratic front trifonov said friday if we arrive at this 
possibility it should be a government of nonpartisan experts 
such a solution would be a coalition through the backdoor 
said a western diplomat saturday who insisted on anonymity 
